{"tid":1472832,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣圖集中post","createTime":"2019-08-14T16:29:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T16:37:07.000Z","uid":16959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a07de6b59b8da3704dd11b504cc6591bd8c7f5aa","tid":1472832,"uid":16959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:29:05.000Z","msg":"今日大陸人開始係ig上反攻<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我地唔可以連ig 都輸埋<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家po文宣po係ig post 到<br />\n加番同香港有關嘅hashtags <br />\n最後轉做public </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n同埋發覺文宣圖唔太集中<br />\n可能有好多手足想搵圖都唔知去邊到搵<br />\n所以麻煩手足集中post 文宣到係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3337e04156988e4649a67f6ae652db2701896188","tid":1472832,"uid":16959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0beaf92a14c0fcd41d73fc0a736c4821fb32ecf0","tid":1472832,"uid":16959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:32:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f4cb1b58eb20716a0de1c5c043990e9854f7d6c","tid":1472832,"uid":165925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:33:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vat3